    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Yes, that was the idea, that the value will change when you refine to make it impossible to have that refinement, basically like how it would be with a slider. I understand that you might want to disable this behaviour though, you should be able to override the default slot, with the input, but without the validation attributes. \r\n\r\nIf you find a nice way to have a property for this which would look good, I'd accept the PR too",
